data.description:
Charming gated cottage neighborhood, unique to the Foley area. Family oriented. Great sense of community. Fantastic neighbors. Community salt water pool, community clubhouse (free bookings) community fitness center. 4 bed, 3 full bath. Granite throughout. Furniture negotiable. Showings to start Monday June 28th. Open house Saturday  July 10th 1-4pm. Must show pre-qualification letter or proof of funds for viewing. P.S. Must love roses and hydrangeas! Drip line irrigation installed. 
Quick access to HWY 59 & Beach Express. 
For questions or viewing appointments call or message Jessica at 251-978-3200. 
Good resale value. Homes in this neighborhood go quickly!
